{"tid":2500410,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"舖頭比錯你份章魚燒前面嗰個人 前面個人走咗之後先返舖頭話比錯咗","createTime":"2021-04-22T15:02:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T15:46:18.000Z","uid":100227,"like":3,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"72a25c971b4ed1090a716086858affff6595442c","tid":2500410,"uid":100227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:02:11.000Z","msg":"然後舖頭照比返人哋拎錯嗰盒你 <br />\n你仲會唔會要? 定叫佢退錢/整過盒?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> - 要 照食 驚乜撚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> - 屌你老母比二手嘢我? 點知前面條撚屌對盒章魚燒做過d乜"},{"pid":"598b986a17679606be83162850de0eb260d3f269","tid":2500410,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:04:01.000Z","msg":"癡線 嗰條友有武肺咁點纂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e44a70d5cc506ddba9597182ded80fd22a66db91","tid":2500410,"uid":221125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:04:58.000Z","msg":"佢做錯野 點解要我受？"},{"pid":"77faa686fa54040d1486f98b8dc33f1c4f0d3f2d","tid":2500410,"uid":44440,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:07:16.000Z","msg":"經驗老到嘅整過盒都唔係好耐啫，我會等下一盒<br />\n<br />\n我早排去美孚，果頭有間食店新開張，諗住試吓啲章魚燒，點知我企撚咗起碼40分鐘先有野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔識整野食唔好開鋪啦，一係train好啲員工先開鋪啦，整章魚燒一路燒一路係咁加粉漿，痴撚線"},{"pid":"d083021a75afa916fd7cd5f6ec207ccdd75f55f6","tid":2500410,"uid":100227,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e44a70d5cc506ddba9597182ded80fd22a66db91","tid":2500410,"uid":221125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:04:58.000Z","msg":"佢做錯野 點解要我受？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:08:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就係想睇下有幾多人真係會出聲<br />\n有時去餐廳食飯都係咁 上菜上咗去隔離枱 <br />\n跟住隔離枱d港女個個唔戴口罩 吹咗勁耐水先知唔係佢哋<br />\nd樓面有時會側側膊拎返入廚房扮嘢 再拎返同一份比你<br />\n你哋見到係咪都會屌?<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fcf3badeca2e1c10f1d5e637fc8cecb8b49f69d","tid":2500410,"uid":60313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:08:26.000Z","msg":"即場請返鋪頭食，唔食就屌鳩佢係咪驚唔撚食？<br />\n你地都唔撚敢食點解要比盒野我？<br />\n<br />\n如果佢地食左，可以選擇比錢買多盒或者走人<br />\n之後話佢地聽，頭先條友除口罩嗅左兩野咳左幾聲<br />\n叫佢地留意下身體。"},{"pid":"5cc8b4e51c157d9a246564e4aeca8604685eedf7","tid":2500410,"uid":100227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77faa686fa54040d1486f98b8dc33f1c4f0d3f2d","tid":2500410,"uid":44440,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:07:16.000Z","msg":"經驗老到嘅整過盒都唔係好耐啫，我會等下一盒<br />\n<br />\n我早排去美孚，果頭有間食店新開張，諗住試吓啲章魚燒，點知我企撚咗起碼40分鐘先有野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔識整野食唔好開鋪啦，一係train好啲員工先開鋪啦，整章魚燒一路燒一路係咁加粉漿，痴撚線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:09:49.000Z","msg":"你唔出聲實比返同一盒你 唔比你 都會比下一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪前狗仔隊開嗰間? 岩岩上完飲食男女"},{"pid":"c667c18b903e80b297050a4c1920b2771a66547b","tid":2500410,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d083021a75afa916fd7cd5f6ec207ccdd75f55f6","tid":2500410,"uid":100227,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e44a70d5cc506ddba9597182ded80fd22a66db91","tid":2500410,"uid":221125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:04:58.000Z","msg":"佢做錯野 點解要我受？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:08:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就係想睇下有幾多人真係會出聲<br />\n有時去餐廳食飯都係咁 上菜上咗去隔離枱 <br />\n跟住隔離枱d港女個個唔戴口罩 吹咗勁耐水先知唔係佢哋<br />\nd樓面有時會側側膊拎返入廚房扮嘢 再拎返同一份比你<br />\n你哋見到係咪都會屌?<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/unwell.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T15:11:29.000Z","msg":"d樓面有時會側側膊拎返入廚房扮嘢 